'''Iserukiramuco du Cinéma Africain de Khouribga''' ( '''FCAK''' ) cyangwa '''iserukiramuco rya sinema nyafurika i Khouribga''' ni iserukiramuco  rya sinema nyafurika ryabereye i Khouribga muri [[Maroke|Maroc]] . Ryashinzwe mu 1977, <ref name="Carter2009">https://books.google.com/books?id=PByNqtLQo8QC&pg=PA130</ref> ni rimwe mu minsi mikuru ya firime ya kera kandi ikomeye muri [[Maroc]]. <ref name="Gugler2011">https://books.google.com/books?id=UQ9zsiRnQQMC&pg=PA326</ref> <ref name="Shafto">Sally Shafto, [https://www.africanfilmny.org/2014/it-all-began-in-khouribga-the-15th-festival-du-cinema-africain-de-khouribga/ It all began in Khouribga: the 15th Festival du Cinéma Africain de Khouribga], ''Senses of Cinema'', No. 64 (September 2012). Republished online, [[African Film Festival, Inc.]], 2014. Accessed 25 November 2019.</ref>

== Amateka ==
Kuva mu 1967, club ya sinema yariho muri Khouribga, ifite abanyamuryango 200 bakora kandi berekanwa buri cyumweru.  Mu 1977, iyobowe na Noureddine Saïl, ihuriro ry’igihugu ry’amafirime ya sinema muri Maroc (FNCCM) ryafashije gutunganya '''Rencontres Cinematographiques de Khouribga''' . Ikipe ya sinema yaho yemeje ko ikomeza kubaho. Kubera ko inganda zikomeye za Khouribga ari  Ubucukuzi bwa fosifate, iyi club yabonye inkunga mu biro bya Fosifati. Iyobowe n’umuryango mpuzamahanga wa Sinema ya gatatu, club ya sinema yemeje ko iserukiramuco ryibanze kuri Afurika . <ref name="Carter2009" />

Inama ya gatatu ya '''Afurika ya Film ya Khouribga''' yabaye kuva ku ya 2–9 Mata 1988. Hateganijwe ingengo y’imari 900.000 (amafaranga 630.000), ubutumire bwahawe abenegihugu 100 n’abanyamahanga bagera kuri 30 baturutse mu bihugu by’abarabu, Uburayi na Afurika. Abaminisitiri bane ba guverinoma bitabiriye iryo funguro rikomeye, kandi abitabiriye nibura 50.000 bareba firime zo mu bihugu 14. Inama ya kane yabaye ku ya 17-24 Werurwe 1990.  Inama ya gatandatu yabaye kuva ku ya 26 Werurwe kugeza ku ya 2 Mata 1994. <ref>''FESPACI News: Newsletter of the African Film-maker'', 1994, pp.12, 14</ref>

Kuva mu 2004 FCAK iyobowe na Fondasiyo, Nourddine Saïl aba Perezida na Lahoussaine N'douf nk'umuyobozi mukuru. <ref name="Shafto">Sally Shafto, [https://www.africanfilmny.org/2014/it-all-began-in-khouribga-the-15th-festival-du-cinema-africain-de-khouribga/ It all began in Khouribga: the 15th Festival du Cinéma Africain de Khouribga], ''Senses of Cinema'', No. 64 (September 2012). Republished online, [[African Film Festival, Inc.]], 2014. Accessed 25 November 2019.</ref>

